Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.86,0:04:38.68,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,I need to take care of something first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.64,0:05:02.29,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:10.12,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,Look Ruby, I really don't want to talk about it, okay?
