Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.78,0:05:16.49,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:18.90,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,Hey Weiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:20.38,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,Did you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:35.57,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,I know she's our teammate,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:38.07,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,but I'm not just going to change my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:40.14,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:42.94,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,I don't think you know what it's like to be left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.22,0:05:44.84,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,You have a giant family, 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:46.86,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,recitals to perform at,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:48.30,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,dinners to attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:51.15,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,I didn't have any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:53.25,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,My mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:54.42,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,...left me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.11,0:05:56.82,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,Ruby's mom left too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:06:00.93,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,Tai was always busy with school and Ruby couldn't even talk yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:03.69,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,I had to pick up the pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.04,0:06:06.18,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,I had to keep things together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.54,0:06:07.52,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,Alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:13.54,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,Weiss, if you have something to say, then say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:22.29,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,When I was ten, my dad finally admitted to my mom that the only reason he married her
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:24.28,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,was for the family name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:27.63,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,It was actually on my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:29.81,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,He missed the big dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:30.79,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,she got mad,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:32.52,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,he finally snapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:36.62,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,I think she already knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:39.31,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,Looking back, I think I knew too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:43.38,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,But hearing him say it finally pushed her over the edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:51.58,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,First it was separate lunches and dinners,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:54.16,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,opposite balconies at my recitals,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:06:57.52,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,a glass of wine here, a glass of wine there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:01.48,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,Then, it was no dinners,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:03.06,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,no recitals,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.24,0:07:05.13,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,a bottle of wine here and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.39,0:07:07.16,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,well, you get the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:09.74,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:12.74,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have assumed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:16.76,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,You're right though. I don't know loneliness like you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:19.04,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,I have my own version.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:20.58,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,And,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:22.93,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,I'll bet Blake has her own version too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:25.12,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,She doesn't have to be alone though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:26.83,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,I was here for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:28.28,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,We all were!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:31.06,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,She {\i1}chose{\i0} to leave us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:33.80,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,Why do you think she did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:40.57,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,The entire time Blake was at Beacon, she was afraid to open up to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.83,0:07:45.09,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,She tried to keep her past separated from us. She tried to protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.47,0:07:48.49,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,Eventually, those walls she put up came down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:50.80,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,And the moment they did,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:54.03,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,the one thing she was afraid of actually happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:56.61,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,The universe proved her right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.15,0:07:58.94,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,No one blamed her for anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:01.64,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,If she had just talked to us, she would've known that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:04.36,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,How could I be there for her if she doesn't let me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:08.74,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,What if I needed her here for me?
