Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:17.16,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,I wish she hadn't left too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:23.24,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,The only thing we can do now is be there for her when she's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.34,0:08:25.47,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,When she comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:30.81,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,{\i1}If{\i0} she comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:32.16,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,{\i1}She will.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:35.54,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,Yang...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:38.65,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,You, Ruby, and even Blake
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:43.13,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,are more like family to me than my brother or even my own father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:45.77,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,I would do anything for you three,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:48.48,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,and I'm willing to bet Blake feels the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:51.60,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,So, when she's ready,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.02,0:08:54.37,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,I'll be there for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.57,0:08:56.36,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:08:58.94,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,...I know we're not as close,...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:00.18,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,...but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:02.94,Default,Weiss,0,0,0,,I'm here for you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.72,0:09:10.82,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,Is, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:12.31,Default,Ruby,0,0,0,,everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:16.51,Default,Yang,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.78,0:09:29.63,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,Ilia?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:31.94,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:44.12,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,Ilia,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.74,0:09:47.58,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,I know you're scared, but you don't have to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:50.33,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,My family and I, we can keep you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.71,0:09:52.70,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.95,0:09:59.30,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,You can make it up to me by helping us stop Corsac and Fennec.
