Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:52.56,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,I am sorry it has to be this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:55.30,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,but you and your family are holding the Faunus back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.75,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,Because we're trying to protect people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:11:02.65,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,In what world do you live in where attacking the innocent is the right thing to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:04.51,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,The same one as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:07.96,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,There's no such thing as innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:12.46,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,There's no right thing to do! Only what's best for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:14.92,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,There's the humans that still hate the Faunus,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:18.82,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,and there's the others who stand by and let the hate happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.68,0:11:21.45,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,{\i1}But you know what snuffs out hate?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:23.64,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,Fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:27.54,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,I don't like hurting people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:29.50,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,But I'll tell you this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:32.08,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,...it's gotten us results.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:34.63,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:36.90,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,look where it's gotten you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:45.95,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,We all have to make sacrifices for the greater good,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.55,0:11:48.27,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,no matter how much it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:52.53,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,And you think killing me is really for the greater good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:11:54.48,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.41,0:11:57.53,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,but getting rid of your family is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:01.57,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,You wouldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.43,0:12:04.36,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,You can't! I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:05.98,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.56,0:12:08.34,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,That's why you're being sent to Mistral.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:09.88,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,To Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:13.40,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,Ilia, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:16.43,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,You don't have to do this. This isn't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:17.76,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,Yes. {\1a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&}It. Is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.76,0:12:18.45,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,Yes. It. {\1a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&}Is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:19.18,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,Yes. It. Is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.94,0:12:24.97,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,But I guess back then you were just too busy falling for Adam to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:31.84,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,I was always jealous of the way you looked at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:35.23,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,I wanted you to look at me that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:40.18,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,But we can't always get what we want!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.16,0:12:43.72,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,Yuma, with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:45.20,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,You two,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.46,0:12:46.67,Default,Ilia,0,0,0,,get her to the docks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:51.04,Default,Trifa,0,0,0,,Let's go, traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.40,0:12:53.26,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:55.93,Default,Trifa,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.98,0:13:05.18,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,Thanks for the backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.75,0:13:07.89,Default,Sun,0,0,0,,Thanks for the invitation. You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:09.59,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.94,0:13:12.24,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,You heard Ilia, my family is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.30,0:13:13.77,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,Call the police and let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:15.46,Default,Sun,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:20.76,Default,Blake,0,0,0,,Come on, mom, pick up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:29.92,Default,Guard,0,0,0,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:42.61,Default,Kali,0,0,0,,Get out of my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.12,0:13:43.66,Default,Kali,0,0,0,,Ghira!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:13:59.70,Default,Ghira,0,0,0,,Go find my wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:17.40,Default,Corsac,0,0,0,,I believe it's time our dear chieftain stepped down, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.88,0:14:21.35,Default,Fennec,0,0,0,,Yes brother, I'm afraid I'm inclined to agree.
